THE GAME
--------

  `Knight' is a Workbench game where you move a Knight on a chess
board, the goal is to go to all the tiles of the board. You
cannot go to a tile you already passed. You move the Knight the
same way as you do in the chess game, that is, an "L" move:
2 spaces horizontally and 1 space vertically, or 1 space
horizontally and 2 spaces vertically.

  Happy Knight'ing!

P.S.: If you want to have a solution to the game, please download
      "SolveKnight.lha" by Ventzislav Tzvetkov:

http://aminet.net/game/hint/SolveKnight.lha

